    <etym xml:lang="ru">Вероятно/ из %iva%i+%ik%i, ср. с одной стороны <mentioned xml:lang="ae"
                ><lang/><w>vā</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"
        ><lang/><w>vā</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"
                    ><lang/><w>*vā(β')</w><gloss><q>или</q></gloss></mentioned>, с другой —
            <mentioned xml:lang="sla"><lang/><w>i</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ru"
                ><lang/><w>и</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">, соединительный союз</note><note
                type="comment" xml:lang="en">, coordinating conjunction</note></mentioned>. Для
        сращения двух союзов ср. хотя бы <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/><w>или</w><note
                type="comment" xml:lang="ru">из %iи%i + %iли%i</note><note type="comment"
                xml:lang="en">from %ii%i + %ili%i</note></mentioned>. Начальное %iv%i, подверженное
        отпадению (ср. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_Acyrūxs"/>), было „спасено“ протетическим
        %iæ%i-.</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">Probably, it is derived from %iva%i+%ik%i, cf. on the one hand <mentioned
            xml:lang="ae"><lang/><w>vā</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"
            ><lang/><w>vā</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"
                    ><lang/><w>*vā(β')</w><gloss><q>или</q></gloss></mentioned>, and on the other
        hand — <mentioned xml:lang="sla"><lang/><w>i</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ru"
                ><lang/><w>и</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">, соединительный союз</note><note
                type="comment" xml:lang="en">, coordinating conjunction</note></mentioned>. As for
        the fusion of two conjunctions, cf. at least <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/><w>ili</w><note
                type="comment" xml:lang="ru">из %iи%i + %iли%i</note><note type="comment"
                xml:lang="en">from %ii%i + %ili%i</note></mentioned>. The initial %iv%i, which is
        subject to the loss (cf. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_Acyrūxs"/>), was “saved” by a
        prothetic %iæ%i-.</etym>
</entry>
